Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:56.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HAD034D&}互相起誓的那天虛假的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:03:00.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H2676F9&}跨越這個殘酷的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:05.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HD37427&}就用吞噬一切的業火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:10.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}將你的痛楚一腳踢開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:14.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}正確與錯誤 可能與不可能
